@startuml TrainingJob State Diagram

[*] --> CREATED : TrainingJobBuilder.build()\n[all required fields present]

CREATED --> RUNNING : POST /api/jobs/{id}/start\n[job exists and is CREATED]

RUNNING --> COMPLETED : All results received\nand aggregation successful\n[evaluationMetric computed]

RUNNING --> FAILED : Worker failure with no\navailable replacement workers\nOR DataFrame empty after preprocessing\nOR aggregation error

CREATED --> FAILED : Validation error\nduring start

COMPLETED --> [*]
FAILED --> [*]

RUNNING : entry / notify observers(RUNNING)
RUNNING : do / track pending worker results
COMPLETED : entry / persist metric + predictions
COMPLETED : entry / notify observers(COMPLETED)
FAILED : entry / persist failureReason
FAILED : entry / notify observers(FAILED)

@enduml
